        <p id="main">Antalya is one of the biggest cities in Turkey and is probably the country’s most significant vacationist hotspot after Istanbul. Traveling to Antalya as a tourist, however, requires a little preparation prior to a visit.</p>
        <h2><em>Historical And Cultural Attraction’s Around Antalya:</em></h2>
        
